      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving naturally aspirated performance, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. The mechanical integrity is absolute; proactive maintenance includes a full rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe carrier to mitigate common chassis fatigue. Power is channeled through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-Differential lock. The exterior maintains its factory-original finish with no orange peel or oxidation, while the cabin features pristine Nappa leather and an instrument cluster free of pixel degradation. Suspension kinematics remain factory-true, offering the sharp turn-in and balanced damping characteristic of a showroom-fresh M-car. Documented service history confirms a life of meticulous preventative care.",
